🔄 4️⃣ Flow of Execution
On System Boot:

main.exe starts

Wake listener thread starts

Tray icon loads

Window hidden

When user says:

“Hello Charlie”

Wake word detected →

show_window()

speak()

UI opens

User gives command →

Frontend sends to /command →

Backend routes →

AI/system executes →

Response returned →

TTS speaks

